<div id="pf464c" class="pf w66 h2f7" data-page-no="464c"><div class="pc pc464c w66 h2f7"><div class="t m1ed xa8 h5 y2f7f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 11 September 7-13 </div><div class="t m2dc x18 h12b y2c70 ff4 fs4b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">E </div><div class="t m5 xc5 h12b y2c70 ff4 fs4b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t ma42 x7c hc2 y2c70 ff1 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ith2 0</div><div class="t m2ac3 x2b hc2 y2c70 ff1 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m19e1 x58 hc2 y2c70 ff1 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">02E[lear </div><div class="t m758 xc3 h5 y2a99 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Is any sick among you? let him call </div><div class="t m298 xd6 h5 y2bcb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the elders of the church; and let </div><div class="t mfb xd6 h5 y2b8b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them pray over him, anointing him </div><div class="t mb85 xd6 h5 y28ea ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with oil in the name of the Lord: and </div><div class="t mf1 xd6 h5 y23bb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the prayer of faith shall save the sick, </div><div class="t ma45 xd6 h5 y23a2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the Lord shall raise him up; and if </div><div class="t m7f3 xd6 h5 yfc4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he have committed sins, they shall be </div><div class="t mcdd xd6 h5 yc6e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forgiven him. Confess your faults one </div><div class="t m417 xd6 h5 y119 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to another, and pray one for another, </div><div class="t ma87 xd6 h5 y20fe ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that ye may be healed. The effectual </div><div class="t m244 xd6 h5 y12c2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fervent prayer of a righteous man </div><div class="t mcf6 xd6 h5 y170 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">availeth much&quot; (James 5:14-16). </div><div class="t m2c3 xb4 h35 y1f0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One of Job&apos;s major problems was </div><div class="t m35c xd6 h35 y360 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical illness. The record says, </div><div class="t m234 xd6 h35 y20e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Satan left the Lord&apos;s presence and </div><div class="t m335 xd6 h35 y5b3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">made sores break out all over Job&apos;s </div><div class="t m719 xd6 h35 y377 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">body&quot; (Job 2:7, TEV). Job refers to his </div><div class="t m2d7 xd6 h35 y9e3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical suffering in chapter 7, verses </div><div class="t ma0e xd6 h35 y5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 through 5: </div><div class="t m728 xb4 h35 yda ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Month after month I have nothing </div><div class="t m6a5 x17 h35 y1d2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to live for; </div><div class="t mbe2 x4 h35 y22d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">night after night brings me grief. </div><div class="t m1 xb4 h35 y2b9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When I lie down to sleep, the hours </div><div class="t m7ba x17 h35 y586 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">drag; </div><div class="t m6dd x4 h35 ybc7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I toss all night and long for dawn. </div><div class="t m5f4 xb4 h35 yac5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">My body is full of worms; </div><div class="t m272 x4 h35 y1be ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it is covered with scabs; </div><div class="t m1344 xbd h35 y134c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pus runs out of my sores&quot; (TEV). </div><div class="t mb99 x20 h35 y2b2d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">And again, &apos; At night my bones all </div><div class="t m82f xaf h35 y2bbb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ache; the pain that gnaws me never </div><div class="t m1b1 x2b h35 y2b9c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stops&quot; (Job 30:17, TEV). </div><div class="t m2ab x20 h35 y2890 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job was one of millions who have </div><div class="t m347 x2b h35 y243d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffered physical pain. The alleviation </div><div class="t m78a x2b h35 y238f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of human suffering has become a </div><div class="t m699 x2b h35 y44e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gigantic enterprise. Yet suffering </div><div class="t m533 x2b h35 y32e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">continues to make life hard for the </div><div class="t m87b x2b h35 y9cb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human race. </div><div class="t me5 x20 h35 y2026 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The ministry of Jesus brought hope </div><div class="t m229 x2b h35 y27f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the sufferer. One of His main </div><div class="t ma99 x2b h35 y23f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">activities was the healing of the sick. </div><div class="t m1b7 x2b h35 y4d2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whithersoever he entered, into </div><div class="t m782 x2b h35 y314 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">villages, or cities, or country, they laid </div><div class="t m6d2 x2b h35 y9e1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sick in the streets, and besought </div><div class="t m214 x2b h35 y2fc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him that they might touch if it were but </div><div class="t m81c x2b h35 y51 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the border of his garment: and as </div><div class="t ma35 x2b h35 y4ca ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many as touched him were made </div><div class="t me19 x2b h35 y378 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whole&quot; (Mark 6:56). </div><div class="t m30a x58 h35 y151 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The apostles of Jesus received </div><div class="t m43f x2b h35 y583 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power to continue this healing </div><div class="t m8ad x2b h35 y335 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ministry, and it became an important </div><div class="t m3c5 x2b h35 y2dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">function of the early church. It is listed </div><div class="t m762 x2b h35 y8f7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as one of the gifts of the Spirit. </div><div class="t m8b9 x58 h35 y2ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our present day, much is said </div><div class="t m96c x2b h35 yb8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about &quot;faith healing.&quot; Popular books </div><div class="t m5d4 x2b h35 y31b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by faith healers recount story after </div><div class="t m879 x2b h35 y104 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">story of successful healings. Other </div><div class="t m8b9 x2b h35 y998 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">observersjpoint to a much larger </div><div class="t m993 x2b h35 y159 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">number of attempted but </div><div class="t mb47 x2b h35 y33b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unsuccessful &quot;cures.&quot; </div><div class="t m787 x58 h35 y407 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The purpose of this lesson is to </div><div class="t m1471 x2b h35 y1074 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">survey the concept of divine </div><div class="t m1a1 x2b h35 y409 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">healing—or faith healing as it is often </div><div class="t m751 x2b h35 y69 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">called—and to endeavor to come to an </div><div class="t m429 x2b h35 ya59 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">understanding of this subject that will </div><div class="t m977 x2b h35 y10e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be useful to Christians in our day. </div><div class="t m558 x2b h5 yeb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x2b h5 y184 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m6f1 x5a h5 y9e8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Investment in Man </div><div class="t mb67 x5a h5 y201 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 1:26; 2:7) </div><div class="t m558 x2b h5 y713 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mfb x5a h5 y712 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Desire to Heal </div><div class="t m109 x5a h5 y165 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:28) </div><div class="t mb7 x2b h5 y4c6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m9b9 x5a h5 y8a9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Faith and Healing </div><div class="t m57d x5a h5 y1e4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 5:15) </div><div class="t m1ce x2b h5 y42e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m7d0 x5a h5 y42d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Love and Healing </div><div class="t m5e1 x5a h5 y49e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 20:30-34) </div><div class="t m8a8 x2b h5 y2027 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m4cd x5a h5 yc73 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Goodness and Healing </div><div class="t m57d x5a h5 y5be ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 5:16) </div><div class="t m2ef x2b h5 y2037 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m7d4 x5a h5 y2f5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Gift of the Spirit </div><div class="t mb10 x5a h5 y10a6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:4, 8, 9) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
